    section.theProblem.container
      .theProblem__wrapper
        h2.theProblem__title.title--h2.title The Problem

        p.text.theProblem__text Beneath the flashy homepages of your favorite sites lurk Hooli™ and other evil  corporations out to hoard and sell your most personal data.

        p.text.theProblem__text What was built to be the ultimate platform for the free sharing of knowledge has turned into a money-hungry monster feasting on our privacy and freedom.

        p.text.theProblem__text But fear not, for Pied Piper has the answer! And it’s simple:</br> An autonomous peer-to-peer network featuring distributed storage powered by universal compression, accelerated scheduling allocation, and end-to-end encryption.

        p.text.theProblem__text Put even simpler — <b>it’s the internet, completely decentralized</b>.

