        img.piperCoin__logo(src="/images/PPC_Logo.png" alt="PPC_Logo.png")

        p.text.piperCoin__text Piper's new internet is built for users, by users. You supply the storage, compute,  and networking resources that power our entire decentralized web.

        p.text.piperCoin__text Now there's a way to give credit where credit is due. Compute credit, that is! The more you share your device resources, the more PiedPiperCoin you receive

        p.text.piperCoin__text Whether you're a developer with an app ready for market, or just an Average Joe with a smartphone you'll love all you can do with PiedPiperCoin.

